      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not suitable for daily driving without major repairs. The engine suffers from a heavy knock and significant oil consumption, while the transmission slips noticeably between gears. The body has visible rust and several dents, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear. This is an ideal project for a mechanic or someone looking for a donor vehicle for parts.",
