    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of this car, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly pristine condition\u2014spotless inside and out, with everything working perfectly. It\u2019s been my baby, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much. You won't find one cleaner than this! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43900.0,
