      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade E46 M3, presenting in concours-level condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a limited-slip M-variable differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed to the highest standard: the VANOS system has been fully bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has received proactive reinforcement for optimal torsional rigidity. The factory finish remains flawless with no signs of oxidation, while the interior retains its original tactile integrity with zero bolster wear. This is a turn-key example of the ultimate driving machine, preserved for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
