    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin smells factory-fresh; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear on the bolsters or creasing, while the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of every service record performed exclusively at the authorized dealership, including a recent major interval service and full fluid flush. The engine bay is pristine, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of road wear or debris. With exceptionally low mileage and a flawless history, this is quite simply the finest example currently on the market\u2014a turn-key collector piece for the most discerning enthusiast.",
